OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fwith late sunny spells this evening,
OL,7,Fany showers in the west dying out.
OL,8,FTurning rather cloudy through the
OL,9,Fnight with patchy rain arriving in the
OL,10,Fwest towards dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FOvercast with patchy rain
OL,13,Fwhich may turn occasionally heavy for
OL,14,Fa time. Moray will see the best of the
OL,15,Fdrier and brighter conditions. Fresh
OL,16,Fwinds, strong on the east coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
